# Face Detection
Security is very important in every organization, to protect every important data and valuable things we need to have reliable security system to help us. The adoption of Face detection that allow only few people in its dataset will surely provide an even greater level of security.

## Data Acquisition

We write the python file named "Create_dataset.py" that uses a webcam to detect faces using haar cascade and use draw the bounding box around the face then, we capture the face 60 pics.

## Data preparation

When we run the "Create_dataset.py"  it will create a new folder inside the dataset named "New person" so,  we will change its name to our name to be a label. After we crop the face that detected , we change them to grayscale and then resize to 130*100 pixel.

## Model training

**LBPHFaceRecognizer** - labels the pixels of an image by thresholding the neighborhood of each pixel and considers the result as a binary number, then we plot eact part of histrogram and arrange their to a histrogram chart so, it make our model can find the pattern and bring that to be a features.

## Model inference

-   Stand in front of the webcam.
-   Run the create_dataset.py
-   Change folder name to your name.
-   Run Face_rec_offline.py
